Richard Neill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Neill 0 Richard Neill (November 12, 1875 – April 8, 1970) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 130 films between 1911 and 1951. He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania and died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles. Richard_Neill ( November_12_,_1875 – April_8_,_1970 ) was an_American_actor of the_silent_era .
